br.com.gamemods.nbtmanipulator

Class NbtList<T extends NbtTag>

  • NbtTag
    • br.com.gamemods.nbtmanipulator.NbtList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -

    The type of the tag that will be wrapped. class NbtEnd and class NbtTag are not valid.


    public class NbtList<T extends NbtTag>
extends NbtTag

    A tag which contains a MutableList structure of class NbtTags. All items in the list must have the same class. Null values in the list are not allowed. The tags in the list will be linked so any modification will also change this tag contents.

    See Also:
    MutableList, class NbtTag
